{"tid":2011082,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家可唔可以齊心先收左又一城同SHK𣄃下商場皮先","createTime":"2020-05-10T18:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T00:41:06.000Z","uid":24178,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cfacfe82bb774b0e8d4403e35ea42cbb9b8c54ef","tid":2011082,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"集中搞幾個商場<br />\n不裝修不屌狗<br />\n聚人唱歌口號直到有狗來<br />\n狗一到就散<br />\n<br />\n覺得好左膠唔夠勇武？<br />\n<br />\n呢個係經濟戰既一大元素<br />\n比你入去燒一間360仲有效<br />\n<br />\n總之mark實一個商場每晚準時8點就和你sing <br />\n雖然一兩個禮拜唔會見成效<br />\n但就係要一路搞落去先會有可能要佢零生意齋輸租<br />\n<br />\n要做到 又一城= 示威區 你唔係示威就唔好去既形象<br />\n<br />\n講又一城係因為佢放狗入去果一幕真係記一世"},{"pid":"4ed8a61c1df8a8cfc45a88d2e838338fed2f906d","tid":2011082,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:34:25.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律<br />\n收埋佢地皮"},{"pid":"a68254ed0bfbde442c843ab3aa4195351e28331b","tid":2011082,"uid":143151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T19:42:19.000Z","msg":"其實真<br />\n一定係先集中咗 先會見到成效<br />\n仲有冇關係個啲 就少啲係個到搞"},{"pid":"c7a3cc42de4d054d64d9c946970649364235ed28","tid":2011082,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T19:48:53.000Z","msg":"向藍屍宣傳去又一城 SHK 黨鐵場 = 黃絲暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c7f945bcd8f5fccdc4c02d4ddd011c9adf5c1f","tid":2011082,"uid":63779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T19:51:31.000Z","msg":"唔好默默玩，默到佢真係無人敢去而你再去就商場變MK重演又一城。"},{"pid":"8d19a26e03089a512ad2b6e933def2ebe391c080","tid":2011082,"uid":49685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T19:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93d10b8b6f65919a98ce9350b189ec03bd1409e","tid":2011082,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:05:12.000Z","msg":"逐一擊破好"},{"pid":"bb1d0fc1ae29ccf67fe2b797a82446092b945